lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur manager Mauricio Pochettino believes his squad has enough strength in depth to compete for both domestic and continental honours after his side reached the last 16 of the Europa League on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Pochettino Primes Two-Pronged Attack on Glory for Spurs
